    {
      "segment_id": "58cfcc64",
      "source_content": "---\nid: usewindowdimensions\ntitle: useWindowDimensions\n---",
      "source_content_hash": "55fa41b46d06be825e31c3975917a7fe7821bf0d9e7e6ac5786f8b53da52bc0d",
      "node_type": "yaml",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_58cfcc64"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "40fe0734",
      "source_content": "```tsx\nimport {useWindowDimensions} from 'react-native';\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "d0f6c217fb04d1d30d56097607804e9c413b2c3471ca4ba3bf3614d223f761ea",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_40fe0734"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "7e5c5a39",
      "source_content": "`useWindowDimensions` automatically updates all of its values when screen size or font scale changes. You can get your application window's width and height like so:",
      "source_content_hash": "2d8df21796633d3a41e5aea67de8c64c6c14c0e74ae012a25d3b82d5447b4391",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "`useWindowDimensions` 會在螢幕尺寸或字體縮放比例變更時自動更新所有數值。您可以透過以下方式取得應用程式視窗的寬度和高度："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "ee201347",
      "source_content": "```tsx\nconst {height, width} = useWindowDimensions();\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "fe68db1dc89d2cee3f86b1c2e71fb9a70e4f8191978b5e09f14cd2dc722131a4",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_ee201347"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "cbe57f9d",
      "source_content": "## Example",
      "source_content_hash": "9bf34f44c9d1371f4eda569dfa04ff7830aff81cfa81646e680cef087714cdc1",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "## 範例"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "6e5ba8fb",
      "source_content": "```SnackPlayer name=useWindowDimensions&supportedPlatforms=ios,android\nimport React from 'react';\nimport {View, StyleSheet, Text, useWindowDimensions} from 'react-native';\n\nconst App = () => {\n  const {height, width, scale, fontScale} = useWindowDimensions();\n  return (\n    <View style={styles.container}>\n      <Text style={styles.header}>Window Dimension Data</Text>\n      <Text>Height: {height}</Text>\n      <Text>Width: {width}</Text>\n      <Text>Font scale: {fontScale}</Text>\n      <Text>Pixel ratio: {scale}</Text>\n    </View>\n  );\n};\nconst styles = StyleSheet.create({\n  container: {\n    flex: 1,\n    justifyContent: 'center',\n    alignItems: 'center',\n  },\n  header: {\n    fontSize: 20,\n    marginBottom: 12,\n  },\n});\n\nexport default App;\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "3be885cc7119d08db75ea4d92e5110e09ef7600e1a49acbbd0d914817a1128bb",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_6e5ba8fb"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "6f930b2f",
      "source_content": "## Properties",
      "source_content_hash": "899ecb557156d36aac98f2082474f5ea1e01af3d4a611b79b00dab2a3116aab2",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "## 屬性"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "11c76fcc",
      "source_content": "### `fontScale`",
      "source_content_hash": "61d747519320575cda9b6882a715a4ee77092ab960a066541243642df3d9d6f5",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "### `fontScale`"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "ac961110",
      "source_content": "```tsx\nuseWindowDimensions().fontScale;\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "9bccb3f7abf925e49689bc83383296b40743a0b62a84ddc9df2662e9c72a460f",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_ac961110"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "4d52a261",
      "source_content": "The scale of the font currently used. Some operating systems allow users to scale their font sizes larger or smaller for reading comfort. This property will let you know what is in effect.",
      "source_content_hash": "eae5dbdcbfe93db927d7e48917633d6c0c996c5016a4468cd2041dce33b453dd",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "當前使用的字體縮放比例。部分作業系統允許使用者調整字體大小以提升閱讀舒適度，此屬性將反映實際生效的縮放值。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "069f729e",
      "source_content": "---",
      "source_content_hash": "cb3f91d54eee30e53e35b2b99905f70f169ed549fd78909d3dac2defc9ed8d3b",
      "node_type": "thematicBreak",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "---"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "e912d935",
      "source_content": "### `height`",
      "source_content_hash": "e4fb016c96faca759fece3409dfac1f2604a28231868dee85e3089e499d9d537",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "### `height`"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "750e2f7e",
      "source_content": "```tsx\nuseWindowDimensions().height;\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "880717e3f8e96053e3d79dc28c9b8b52387a7e7600c29603a153e8d85fec9f15",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_750e2f7e"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "0bb95128",
      "source_content": "The height in pixels of the window or screen your app occupies.",
      "source_content_hash": "40e0c2854974815d8cd2f8164ac3295569d29961ae05a79c4a9f7f2dda7c7768",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "應用程式佔用的視窗或螢幕高度（單位：像素）。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "379d3a5b",
      "source_content": "---",
      "source_content_hash": "cb3f91d54eee30e53e35b2b99905f70f169ed549fd78909d3dac2defc9ed8d3b",
      "node_type": "thematicBreak",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "---"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "52388877",
      "source_content": "### `scale`",
      "source_content_hash": "770def4c8f19fb4bcb79d969e3d52e38a5e8cf344362eaf772b9dd096a5454bb",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "### `scale`"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "bc137a19",
      "source_content": "```tsx\nuseWindowDimensions().scale;\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "bc47c190d60d7d48298e7087efad7a419cdc89bbf8e214903e1c4cf78286967c",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_bc137a19"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "afa378f7",
      "source_content": "The pixel ratio of the device your app is running on. The values can be:",
      "source_content_hash": "c1a8881e3a08f8b153f75e7a79674294fca05aba526e8b04b796427e813a4526",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "應用程式運行裝置的像素密度比例，可能值包括："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "1316cb90",
      "source_content": "- `1` which indicates that one point equals one pixel (usually PPI/DPI of 96, 76 on some platforms).\n- `2` or `3` which indicates a Retina or high DPI display.",
      "source_content_hash": "5b56c0fbfe4c8c8fd80f22696988dcdd73ebbc49a04c9c168525dafdaeab0247",
      "node_type": "list",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "- `1`：表示1點等於1像素（通常對應96 PPI/DPI，部分平台為76）\n- `2` 或 `3`：表示Retina或高DPI顯示器"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "678c3938",
      "source_content": "---",
      "source_content_hash": "cb3f91d54eee30e53e35b2b99905f70f169ed549fd78909d3dac2defc9ed8d3b",
      "node_type": "thematicBreak",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "---"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a4bf4268",
      "source_content": "### `width`",
      "source_content_hash": "466da2ad29daff30b425dbfda1b4bbf5a290672ed5b2415e7bbfb14d844dbe75",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "### `width`"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "8c3563d3",
      "source_content": "```tsx\nuseWindowDimensions().width;\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "030117a160c7b257bca1a2a3d153c94ee56a9ac9768ae6db5c7b3ba7f65fd2be",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_8c3563d3"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "0750bfa1",
      "source_content": "The width in pixels of the window or screen your app occupies.",
      "source_content_hash": "13ae736e1d1f1196970a8449a74646970dbe689cd2c772d699e2fb95c8fd2237",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "zh-hant": "應用程式佔用的視窗或螢幕寬度（單位：像素）。"
      }
    }
